ZH: 这个小村庄的居民大多数都生活在贫困中。
EN: Most of the residents in this small village live in poverty.

ZH: 政府正在努力减轻贫困现象。
EN: The government is making efforts to alleviate poverty.

ZH: 我们应该关注贫困地区的教育问题。
EN: We should pay attention to the educational issues in impoverished areas.

ZH: 贫困并不代表一个人的价值。
EN: Poverty does not determine a person's worth.

ZH: 这个项目旨在帮助贫困儿童完成学业。
EN: This project aims to help impoverished children complete their education.

ZH: 学习能够帮助人们摆脱贫困。
EN: Education can help people escape poverty.

ZH: 政府提供了一些补助金来帮助贫困家庭。
EN: The government provides some subsidies to help impoverished families.

ZH: 缺乏教育是导致贫困的一个主要原因。
EN: Lack of education is one of the main causes of poverty.

ZH: 我们应该共同努力，消除贫困现象。
EN: We should work together to eradicate poverty.

ZH: 这个地区的人们每天都在为温饱而奔波，非常贫困。
EN: The people in this region struggle every day for food and are extremely impoverished.

ZH: 他们家境贫困，但却一直都很乐观。
EN: Their family is poor, but they have always remained optimistic.

ZH: 这个家庭靠勤劳和努力逐渐摆脱了贫困。
EN: This family gradually escaped poverty through hard work and effort.

ZH: 他投身于扶贫事业，帮助了许多贫困家庭。
EN: He has dedicated himself to poverty alleviation and has helped many impoverished families.

ZH: 寻找增加农民收入的方法是解决农村贫困的关键。
EN: Finding ways to increase farmers' income is the key to solving rural poverty.

ZH: 这个项目为贫困地区提供了就业机会。
EN: This project provides employment opportunities for impoverished areas.

ZH: 没有人应该因为贫困而受到歧视。
EN: No one should be discriminated against because of poverty.

ZH: 她从小就生活在贫困中，但她坚持奋斗不息。
EN: She has lived in poverty since childhood, but she persists in striving.

ZH: 这个慈善机构致力于帮助贫困妇女获得就业机会。
EN: This charity organization is dedicated to helping impoverished women find employment opportunities.

ZH: 我们应该关注贫困人口的基本需求。
EN: We should focus on the basic needs of the poverty-stricken population.

ZH: 贫困不应该成为一个人成功的障碍。
EN: Poverty should not be a barrier to success for an individual.
